write_up: Lil Tracy and Lil Peep were the greatest rap duo of the decade, besides, I guess, Young Thug and Rich Homie Quan, but even then their interplay has nothing on Lil Tracy/Lil Peep who exchange between themselves so effortlessly it's as if they were the same person. The Nedarb classic production choice of flipping great indie music never turned out better.
lyric: She goin’ home with me tonight, we connect like Wi-Fi
